Insider Activity


Individual




C. Edward Chaplin



Mr. C. E. Chaplin, CFA, is Independent Director at MGIC Investment Corp., Executive Vice President at MBIA, Inc., a Member at Executive Leadership Council, Inc., President, CEO & Chief Administrative Officer at Optinuity Alliance Resources Corp. and Vice Chairman & Chief Financial Officer at MBIA Insurance Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Mortgage Guaranty Insurance Corp., MGIC Investment Corp., Rutgers University Foundation, Rutgers University (New Jersey) and MBIA Insurance Corp. Mr. Chaplin was previously employed as Treasurer & Senior Vice President by Prudential Financial, Inc. He also served on the board at Pruco Life Insurance Co. He received his undergraduate degree from Rutgers University (New Jersey) and a graduate degree from Harvard University.



