C. Edward Chaplin 
Executive Compensation
As Former Chief Financial Officer and Chief Administrative Officer at MBIA INC, C. Edward Chaplin  made $4,713,750 in total compensation.  Of this total $750,000 was received as a salary, $750,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $750,000 was awarded as stock and $2,463,750 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


